Constructor & Destructor Documentation

PostProcessing::PlayerFader::PlayerFader ( PyTypeObject *  pType = &s_type_  ) 

Constructor.

In the constructor, this object checks whether the near-plane clips the player. If so, it adjusts the visibility of the player's model.

PostProcessing::PlayerFader::~PlayerFader (  ) 

Destructor.

In the destructor, the visibility of the player's model is restored.
